Set 1

Sugaree-> Little Red Rooster, Friend Of The Devil, My Brother Esau, Bird Song, Hell In A Bucket-> Deal

Set 2

Touch Of Grey-> Samson & Delilah, To Lay Me Down, Women Are Smarter, Terrapin Station-> Drums-> The Wheel-> I Need A Miracle-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Good Lovin', E: Revolution

reviews.review_text: Hot damn! One of my favorites, and this is a sweet, sweet recording with killer stereo separation, depth and clarity. The performance is heavenly, from cover to cover.
